<p><a name="In_pop_culture" id="In_pop_culture"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Rainbow_Series&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: In pop culture">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">In pop culture</span></h2>
<p>The movie <a href="/wiki/Hackers_(film)" title="Hackers (film)">Hackers</a> contained a reference to the Rainbow Books that showed Dade naming off a series of books, one of them being the Red Book from this series.</p>
